snippet.title: Final Profit: A Shop RPG - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Final Profit is a story-driven management shop-sim RPG.
Buy on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1705140/Final_Profit_A_Shop_RPG/

With incremental growth tied to income and economic systems. Make investments and harsh choices as you explore a world full of secrets, and try to take down the corrupt Bureau of Business!

Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/FinalProfitRPG
Follow on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@finalprofitrpg
Join the Discord: https://discord.com/invite/VX7M58RfJn
Join the Reddit community: https://www.reddit.com/r/FinalProfit/
Website: https://www.finalprofit.com.au/
Support the developer on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/finalprofit
